    <header class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row row-header">
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-7">
            <h1>WIRED Meetings</h1>
            <p>
              We believe that communication should make no diffrentiation , all
              people should have the same oppurtunity in communicating and
              having smooth interviews experience , disablities should never be
              obstacles !
